    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ 关于游戏</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/9f62907ce5e4b2097d1019c64cca713d.poster.avif?t=1726403949\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/9f62907ce5e4b2097d1019c64cca713d.webm?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/9f62907ce5e4b2097d1019c64cca713d.mp4?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《谁是谁？》是一款适合与朋友一起体验的在线派对游戏。<br>找到隐藏于AI角色中的真人，成为最后的幸存者！<br>不过也要小心，千万别暴露自己！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/b0000f365e5ab2b7cd19f2468f2e57e3.poster.avif?t=1726403949\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/b0000f365e5ab2b7cd19f2468f2e57e3.webm?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/b0000f365e5ab2b7cd19f2468f2e57e3.mp4?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>找出隐藏在AI角色中的真人非常重要！<br>但如何隐藏自己也同样重要。<br>请伪装成AI角色瞒过他人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/72381d1878e9923d904f5eaf07569f82.poster.avif?t=1726403949\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/72381d1878e9923d904f5eaf07569f82.webm?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/72381d1878e9923d904f5eaf07569f82.mp4?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>向你走来的是AI角色还是人类？<br>请睁大眼睛寻找可疑的地方！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/8ffd3fc5cb953ca79c8c21fc9aa0fe7a.poster.avif?t=1726403949\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/8ffd3fc5cb953ca79c8c21fc9aa0fe7a.webm?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796200/extras/8ffd3fc5cb953ca79c8c21fc9aa0fe7a.mp4?t=1726403949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>如果感到怀疑，不要犹豫，先进行攻击！<br>因为机会只有一次！<br><br>在激烈的眼色游戏中成为最后的幸存者！<br>将会感受到一种前所未有的刺激感。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ 游戏特点</strong></h2><strong>－多种游戏模式</strong><br>&gt; 警察和小偷模式：<br>博物馆里陈列着大量奇珍异宝！<br>化身小偷，瞒过警察偷走宝物。<br>如果不喜欢，那就化身警察抓住小偷。<br><br>&gt; 个人战：<br>在所有人都伪装成NPC的空间里，寻找行为<br>怪异的人！ 在成为最终胜利者之前，绝不能放松警惕。<br><br>除此之外还有许多模式！<br><br><strong>- 可爱的角色和各种服装</strong><br>&gt; 穿上各种服装，打造属于自己的角色。<br>高画质3D图像更添可爱。",
